quest_title: Which of the following shown particle nature of light?
explanation_txt:
In photoelectric effect, there is one to one ratio of ejected photoelectrons to photons of light. Photoelectrons are not emitted if the energy of each photon is less than work function of metal which is contrary to wave nature of light as energy is spontaneous for a wave. Furthermore, higher value of photoelectricity is obtained for higher intensity of light (more photons =more electrons).

Thus, particle behavior is demonstrated by photo electric effect.
